Third Uncle,

6
00:02:05,710 --> 00:02:06,400
Uncle Yu.

7
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:09,960
I...

8
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:12,190
wanted to go back to my own quarters.

9
00:02:12,190 --> 00:02:14,150
Your quarters aren't in this direction.

10
00:02:14,150 --> 00:02:16,079
Go back to rest since you're drunk.

11
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:17,800
Yes.

12
00:02:18,470 --> 00:02:19,200
Then I'll...

13
00:02:20,850 --> 00:02:21,850
take my leave now.

14
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,130
Why did he drink so much?

15
00:02:32,590 --> 00:02:33,270
Jiuheng,

16
00:02:33,310 --> 00:02:34,520
I won't be escorting you
to the bridal chamber.

17
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:35,240
I'll go keep an eye on him.

18
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:36,440
Okay, go check on him.

19
00:02:36,710 --> 00:02:38,120
May you be blessed with children soon!

20
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:38,590
Xuruo!

21
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:53,930
Third Master...

22
