41
00:05:14,250 --> 00:05:17,710
♪ Beneath the bright moonlight,
you and I stand together ♪

42
00:05:18,770 --> 00:05:22,120
♪ Hand in hand, our love deepens
with each passing year ♪

43
00:05:23,460 --> 00:05:28,180
♪ By your side,
I'll follow wherever your heart leads ♪

44
00:05:29,870 --> 00:05:32,180
♪ Ask the passing time
whether it has forgotten ♪

45
00:05:32,770 --> 00:05:34,360
♪ The moonlight of our first encounter ♪

46
00:05:35,530 --> 00:05:39,010
♪ Year after year,
it etches your likeness ♪

47
00:05:39,870 --> 00:05:42,370
♪ Count the faint shimmer
of the starry river ♪

48
00:05:43,430 --> 00:05:47,030
♪ Yet none compares
to the gentle light in your eyes ♪

49
00:05:48,150 --> 00:05:50,000
♪ At last, I see the galaxy
shimmering and swaying ♪

50
00:05:50,870 --> 00:05:52,590
♪ Reflected in our eyes ♪

51
00:05:53,540 --> 00:05:58,159
♪ I'll be with you forever ♪

52
00:05:59,340 --> 00:06:02,950
♪ And enjoy
the beautiful scenery with you ♪

53
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:06,070
I've been

54
00:06:05,060 --> 00:06:08,860
♪ For all the days of our lives,
our love will endure ♪

55
00:06:06,310 --> 00:06:07,510
meaning to ask you—

56
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:10,070
why do you have

57
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,830
so many scars on your body?

58
00:06:13,870 --> 00:06:15,480
Ever since I've known you,

59
00:06:16,430 --> 00:06:17,270
you've

60
00:06:17,270 --> 00:06:19,270
encountered danger several times.

61
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:23,950
Aren't you a civil official?

62
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:26,520
Why do you keep getting injured?

63
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:27,360
They say,

64
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:29,630
"When civil officials shun greed

65
00:06:29,630 --> 00:06:31,160
and military officials do not fear death,

66
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:33,090
an age of prosperity may yet dawn."

67
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:35,140
But our dynasty is different.

68
00:06:36,159 --> 00:06:38,020
Though it has stood for a century,

69
00:06:39,070 --> 00:06:40,430
it's beginning to show signs

70
00:06:40,430 --> 00:06:42,030
of instability and decline.

71
00:06:42,070 --> 00:06:43,000
Civil officials

72
00:06:43,430 --> 00:06:44,720
must not only refrain from greed

73
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:46,380
but also have no fear of death.

74
00:06:47,310 --> 00:06:48,800
Only then might there still be hope
for the state.

75
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,659
As expected of a Grand Secretary.

76
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,870
You always talk about
the dynasty's grand legacy

77
00:06:52,870 --> 00:06:54,530
and the welfare of the people.

78
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:03,770
I know I was wrong.

79
00:07:04,630 --> 00:07:05,600
I really

80
00:07:05,830 --> 00:07:07,890
didn't care enough about my own life.

81
00:07:08,270 --> 00:07:09,670
But from today onward...

82
00:07:11,430 --> 00:07:13,230
I'll take better care of myself.

83
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,640
Then remember this well:

84
00:07:18,190 --> 00:07:18,950
since

85
00:07:19,830 --> 00:07:20,830
I've married you,

86
00:07:21,430 --> 00:07:23,830
you're only allowed to
stay alive and well.

87
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:27,770
Understood.

88
00:07:42,950 --> 00:07:43,750
What's wrong?

89
00:07:49,430 --> 00:07:50,490
There's something

90
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:52,240
I have to tell you.

91
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:55,820
Marquis Changxing...

92
00:07:56,950 --> 00:07:57,750
passed away

93
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:59,980
in the middle of the night yesterday.

94
00:08:03,430 --> 00:08:04,270
So,

95
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:07,310
the funeral procession we encountered

96
00:08:07,310 --> 00:08:08,910
on South Gate Street earlier

97
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:10,240
was...

98
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:14,940
The court has bestowed 200 taels of gold.

99
00:08:15,480 --> 00:08:16,340
His Majesty has

100
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:19,000
granted an additional
1,000 taels of silver

101
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:21,240
and permitted the funeral vigil
to be held at Xuanmiao Temple.

102
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:22,700
The Ye family should all be

103
00:08:22,830 --> 00:08:24,160
at the temple right now.

104
00:08:27,430 --> 00:08:29,680
Did the court mention anything

105
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:32,039
about Ye Xian inheriting the title?

106
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:33,289
What do you think

107
00:08:34,750 --> 00:08:35,809
is more important—

108
00:08:36,549 --> 00:08:37,809
life, or a noble title?

109
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:42,200
Naturally, life is more important.

110
00:08:47,150 --> 00:08:47,750
His life

111
00:08:48,870 --> 00:08:50,470
should have been preserved.

112
00:09:03,500 --> 00:09:06,240
[Great Merit and High Esteem]

113
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:06,840
[A Legacy of Virtue and Grace]

114
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:19,870
[Spirit Tablet of Ye Guangsheng,
Late Marquis Changxing of Great Yan]

115
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:25,270
Miss Xue.

116
00:09:30,590 --> 00:09:31,520
Why are you here?

117
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:34,520
To offer incense to the Marquis.

118
00:09:34,760 --> 00:09:35,960
If you had come alone,

119
00:09:36,030 --> 00:09:38,030
I might actually have believed you.

120
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:41,000
But now that you've brought
your husband along,

121
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:43,600
I can only assume
you come with bad intentions.

122
00:09:44,710 --> 00:09:45,640
Where is Ye Xian?

123
00:09:55,790 --> 00:09:56,440
Ye Xian.

124
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:03,580
Aren't you here to offer incense?

125
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:04,930
Go ahead.

126
00:10:46,770 --> 00:10:47,770
I have a few words

127
00:10:47,800 --> 00:10:49,100
to say to Young Lord Ye.

128
00:10:49,180 --> 00:10:50,110
Why don't you...

129
00:10:51,010 --> 00:10:52,320
wait outside?

130
00:10:58,550 --> 00:10:59,500
Miss Xue.

131
00:11:13,910 --> 00:11:15,510
Ye Xian, receive the decree.

132
00:11:33,150 --> 00:11:34,690
Marquis Changxing, Ye Guangsheng,

133
00:11:34,610 --> 00:11:37,800
[Imperial Edict]

134
00:11:34,790 --> 00:11:36,080
fought for the country

135
00:11:36,670 --> 00:11:38,630
with loyalty and valor
worthy of commendation.

136
00:11:38,630 --> 00:11:40,140
Upon hearing the sorrowful news,

137
00:11:40,140 --> 00:11:41,390
I am deeply grieved.

138
00:11:42,900 --> 00:11:46,060
[Ye]

139
00:11:48,390 --> 00:11:49,000
Jinzhao.

140
00:11:54,150 --> 00:11:55,150
I don't blame you.

141
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:57,690
You had your own choice to make.

142
00:11:57,910 --> 00:11:59,240
You chose Chen Jiuheng.

143
00:11:59,870 --> 00:12:01,000
Ye Xian, foolish as he is,

144
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:02,400
can only accept his loss.

145
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:06,770
There's no right or wrong in such matters.

146
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:08,280
Even if you blamed me,

147
00:12:09,270 --> 00:12:10,400
I wouldn't be angry.

148
00:12:11,030 --> 00:12:11,600
Why?

149
00:12:12,520 --> 00:12:14,580
Because you truly care about Ye Xian.

150
00:12:19,150 --> 00:12:20,440
I mean it.

151
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:22,440
Thank you

152
00:12:23,560 --> 00:12:25,560
for looking after Ye Xian all along.

153
00:12:26,120 --> 00:12:27,580
You don't need to thank me.

154
00:12:28,870 --> 00:12:30,440
I've just been blind.

155
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:32,390
The day I come to my senses,

156
00:12:32,390 --> 00:12:34,650
I'll walk away without a second thought.

157
00:12:37,870 --> 00:12:38,470
By the way,

158
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:41,390
what does your husband
want to say to Ye Xian?

159
00:12:41,390 --> 00:12:42,270
I have no idea.

160
00:12:43,670 --> 00:12:45,400
An owl visiting in the night—

161
00:12:45,480 --> 00:12:46,480
never a good sign.

162
00:12:48,120 --> 00:12:49,150
That reminds me—

163
00:12:50,150 --> 00:12:51,460
there was a time Ye Xian

164
00:12:51,720 --> 00:12:53,510
saw me together with Yanyun,

165
00:12:55,270 --> 00:12:56,730
and he said the same thing.

166
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:05,670
According to the laws of our dynasty,

167
00:13:05,670 --> 00:13:07,270
his son Ye Xian suffers from illness

168
00:13:07,270 --> 00:13:08,840
and is unfit to inherit the title.

169
00:13:08,840 --> 00:13:11,320
Therefore, the title of
Marquis Changxing is revoked.

170
00:13:11,320 --> 00:13:12,600
Additionally, 200 taels of silver,

171
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:13,910
500 bolts of silk, and one chest of

172
00:13:13,910 --> 00:13:16,240
calligraphy and paintings are bestowed.

173
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:18,560
Receive the decree, Ye Xian.

174
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:25,000
This subject

175
00:13:26,030 --> 00:13:28,030
receives the edict with gratitude.

176
00:13:54,030 --> 00:13:55,030
It was only to be expected

177
00:13:55,030 --> 00:13:57,090
that you wouldn't inherit the title.

178
00:13:57,120 --> 00:13:57,910
Why resort to

179
00:13:57,910 --> 00:13:59,370
such childish theatrics?

180
00:14:04,720 --> 00:14:05,670
His Majesty has another verbal decree

181
00:14:05,670 --> 00:14:06,440
for you.

182
00:14:19,870 --> 00:14:21,440
By His Majesty's verbal decree—

183
00:14:21,440 --> 00:14:23,360
A new Xuanfeng Guard shall be established,

184
00:14:23,360 --> 00:14:24,600
drawing 500 elite troops
carefully selected

185
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:26,960
from the Imperial Guards
to form its ranks.

186
00:14:26,960 --> 00:14:28,490
Ye Xian is hereby appointed

187
00:14:28,630 --> 00:14:30,560
Commander of the Xuanfeng Guards.

188
00:14:31,510 --> 00:14:33,360
He shall command
the Emperor's personal guards

189
00:14:33,360 --> 00:14:34,780
and hold authority over

190
00:14:34,810 --> 00:14:36,630
supervision and interrogation.

191
00:14:36,630 --> 00:14:37,560
So it is decreed.

192
00:14:41,220 --> 00:14:42,510
This subject obeys the decree.

193
00:14:42,510 --> 00:14:44,640
This subject shall not fail in his duty

194
00:14:45,240 --> 00:14:47,370
and will share His Majesty's burdens.

195
00:14:58,270 --> 00:14:59,550
His Majesty has truly gone to
great lengths

196
00:14:59,550 --> 00:15:00,610
for your sake.

197
00:15:01,270 --> 00:15:02,930
Be sure you prove worthy of it.

198
00:15:05,720 --> 00:15:06,440
Thank you.

199
00:15:17,480 --> 00:15:22,440
[Marquis Changxing's Mansion]

200
00:15:24,690 --> 00:15:26,830
[Memorial]

201
00:15:47,910 --> 00:15:54,250
[Memorial]

202
00:15:56,120 --> 00:15:57,000
You mean

203
00:15:57,190 --> 00:15:59,050
His Majesty played the long game—

204
00:15:59,270 --> 00:16:01,030
first agreeing with
the Senior Grand Secretary

205
00:16:01,030 --> 00:16:02,890
to rescind the Ye family's title,

206
00:16:03,240 --> 00:16:05,910
then using the pretext of
unrest within the palace

207
00:16:05,910 --> 00:16:07,320
to force the Senior Grand Secretary into

208
00:16:07,320 --> 00:16:09,250
establishing the Xuanfeng Guard?

209
00:16:09,600 --> 00:16:10,150
Yes.

210
00:16:14,390 --> 00:16:17,250
Ever since
the late Prince Chengqing's rebellion,

211
00:16:17,550 --> 00:16:18,440
the Penal Court

212
00:16:18,870 --> 00:16:19,840
has long been infiltrated by

213
00:16:19,840 --> 00:16:21,770
various factions within the court

214
00:16:21,960 --> 00:16:23,620
and is no longer trustworthy.

215
00:16:23,790 --> 00:16:25,390
The entire court knows this.

216
00:16:26,080 --> 00:16:27,070
And Ye Xian's

217
00:16:27,150 --> 00:16:29,350
loyalty to His Majesty is unshakeable.

218
00:16:29,720 --> 00:16:30,840
Even my mentor

219
00:16:31,510 --> 00:16:32,910
cannot argue otherwise.

220
00:16:33,390 --> 00:16:35,360
So His Majesty came up with this plan—

221
00:16:35,360 --> 00:16:36,620
both to protect Ye Xian

222
00:16:37,080 --> 00:16:37,810
and to secure

223
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:39,800
for himself a personal guard

224
00:16:40,560 --> 00:16:42,420
to keep watch over all officials.

225
00:16:43,870 --> 00:16:45,000
That's quite

226
00:16:45,750 --> 00:16:47,200
the calculated move.

227
00:16:48,270 --> 00:16:48,840
Yes.

228
00:16:49,870 --> 00:16:50,730
His Majesty...

229
00:16:51,720 --> 00:16:52,510
has grown up.

230
00:16:54,730 --> 00:16:58,960
[Happiness]

231
00:16:57,670 --> 00:16:59,120
Please have tea, Mother.

232
00:17:04,339 --> 00:17:13,069
[Happiness]

233
00:17:14,790 --> 00:17:17,140
May you love each other dearly

234
00:17:17,349 --> 00:17:19,280
and soon be blessed with children

235
00:17:19,700 --> 00:17:21,230
to carry on the family line.

236
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:22,550
Yes.

237
00:17:23,240 --> 00:17:24,300
Thank you, Mother.

238
00:17:32,070 --> 00:17:35,270
Second Brother, Second Sister-in-law,
please have tea.

239
00:17:36,510 --> 00:17:37,400
Okay, okay.

240
00:17:38,440 --> 00:17:39,720
My third brother

241
00:17:40,110 --> 00:17:42,270
has always been reserved
yet strong-willed.

242
00:17:42,270 --> 00:17:43,790
Whether in state or family affairs,

243
00:17:43,790 --> 00:17:45,450
he has never once complained.

244
00:17:45,640 --> 00:17:46,640
In the days ahead,

245
00:17:46,720 --> 00:17:48,820
I hope you will take good care of him.

246
00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:51,260
Tend to his needs and care for him well

247
00:17:51,440 --> 00:17:52,880
so that I, as his elder brother,

248
00:17:52,880 --> 00:17:54,440
may feel at ease when away from home.

249
00:17:54,440 --> 00:17:55,720
Why are you being so noisy?

250
00:17:55,720 --> 00:17:56,580
Drink your tea.

251
00:18:00,160 --> 00:18:01,890
Second Brother, I understand.

252
00:18:02,030 --> 00:18:03,490
I'll take good care of him.

253
00:18:03,640 --> 00:18:04,200
Good.

254
00:18:05,070 --> 00:18:05,440
Here,

255
00:18:05,830 --> 00:18:06,690
this is for you.

256
00:18:07,110 --> 00:18:08,640
Thank you, Second Brother,

257
00:18:09,240 --> 00:18:10,570
Second Sister-in-law.

258
00:18:11,920 --> 00:18:12,970
Third Madam,

259
00:18:13,240 --> 00:18:14,300
please have a seat.

260
00:18:28,030 --> 00:18:30,230
Please have tea, Third Sister-in-law.

261
00:18:44,750 --> 00:18:46,610
Thank you, Third Sister-in-law.

262
00:18:48,720 --> 00:18:50,580
Thank you, Third Sister-in-law.

263
00:19:03,030 --> 00:19:04,510
Congratulations, Third Sister-in-law.

264
00:19:04,510 --> 00:19:07,040
Please drink this tea,
Third Sister-in-law.

265
00:19:16,590 --> 00:19:18,450
Thank you, Third Sister-in-law.

266
00:19:20,550 --> 00:19:21,300
Jinzhao,

267
00:19:21,440 --> 00:19:23,100
from now on, we're one family.

268
00:19:26,550 --> 00:19:28,110
Mother and Old Madam Ji

269
00:19:28,110 --> 00:19:29,770
have long been bosom friends.

270
00:19:29,880 --> 00:19:31,230
Now that our two families

271
00:19:31,230 --> 00:19:32,480
have become in-laws as well,

272
00:19:32,480 --> 00:19:34,310
we're truly closer than ever.

273
00:19:34,550 --> 00:19:35,030
Indeed.

274
00:19:35,960 --> 00:19:36,920
Now,

275
00:19:37,350 --> 00:19:39,750
your second sister-in-law
manages the household.

276
00:19:39,750 --> 00:19:41,960
If there's anything you need

277
00:19:42,640 --> 00:19:44,760
or anything you don't understand,

278
00:19:45,310 --> 00:19:47,140
just go to her.

279
00:19:47,310 --> 00:19:48,040
Yes, Mother.

280
00:19:48,720 --> 00:19:49,790
If any maid

281
00:19:49,880 --> 00:19:51,920
or servant gives you trouble,

282
00:19:52,070 --> 00:19:52,830
just tell me.

283
00:19:53,310 --> 00:19:54,770
I'll sort them out for you.

284
00:19:55,440 --> 00:19:56,240
I understand.

285
00:19:56,400 --> 00:19:58,330
Thank you, Second Sister-in-law.

286
00:19:58,550 --> 00:19:59,660
The younger ones

287
00:19:59,720 --> 00:20:01,270
haven't paid their respects
to their aunt yet.

288
00:20:01,270 --> 00:20:01,930
Go quickly.

289
00:20:07,880 --> 00:20:08,650
These two

290
00:20:08,720 --> 00:20:10,790
are my children with your second brother—

291
00:20:10,790 --> 00:20:12,140
Xuansong and Xuanbai.

292
00:20:12,350 --> 00:20:14,350
They came back especially
for the occasion.

293
00:20:14,350 --> 00:20:16,830
Please have tea, Third Aunt.

294
00:20:22,000 --> 00:20:22,930
This is Xuan'an,

295
00:20:23,070 --> 00:20:24,600
Fourth Brother's only son.

296
00:20:24,750 --> 00:20:26,310
He's only just begun his studies.

297
00:20:26,310 --> 00:20:28,160
Please have tea, Auntie Third.

298
00:20:29,030 --> 00:20:30,640
You should call her "Third Aunt."

299
00:20:30,640 --> 00:20:31,920
Third Aunt.

300
00:20:44,720 --> 00:20:46,270
Alright, you may leave now.

301
00:20:47,030 --> 00:20:48,290
Thank you, Third Aunt.

302
00:20:55,750 --> 00:20:56,830
This is Xuanqing.

303
00:20:57,030 --> 00:20:58,030
We've met before.

304
00:21:04,550 --> 00:21:04,960
Right.

305
00:21:05,400 --> 00:21:07,750
When I was still living with
my grandmother in Tongzhou,

306
00:21:07,750 --> 00:21:10,160
Mother and Yanyun both came.

307
00:21:10,350 --> 00:21:11,590
Xuanqing was there too.

308
00:21:11,590 --> 00:21:12,750
Right, right, right.

309
00:21:12,750 --> 00:21:14,060
I remember now.

310
00:21:14,440 --> 00:21:16,400
At your coming-of-age ceremony, right?

311
00:21:16,400 --> 00:21:18,640
Fate truly works in mysterious ways.

312
00:21:21,200 --> 00:21:21,880
Xuanqing.

313
00:21:54,160 --> 00:21:54,620
My Lady!

314
00:21:55,550 --> 00:21:56,010
Well...

315
00:21:56,590 --> 00:21:57,240
Are you alright?

316
00:21:57,240 --> 00:21:57,840
I'm sorry.

317
00:21:58,000 --> 00:21:58,930
I didn't mean it.

318
00:21:59,640 --> 00:22:00,240
Let me see.

319
00:22:01,960 --> 00:22:02,820
You got burned.

320
00:22:03,550 --> 00:22:04,240
I'm fine.

321
00:22:06,680 --> 00:22:08,410
Fetch some Sanhuang Ointment.

322
00:22:09,200 --> 00:22:09,800
It's fine.

323
00:22:10,200 --> 00:22:11,680
The tea was only warm.

324
00:22:14,350 --> 00:22:15,810
Prepare a fresh cup of tea.

325
00:22:16,200 --> 00:22:16,790
No need.

326
00:22:17,440 --> 00:22:19,100
Consider it already offered.

327
00:22:23,200 --> 00:22:23,880
Qingpu,

328
00:22:24,200 --> 00:22:25,300
bring the gift

329
00:22:25,400 --> 00:22:26,270
prepared for Xuanqing.

330
00:22:26,270 --> 00:22:26,750
Yes.

331
00:22:38,750 --> 00:22:39,350
Thank you.

332
00:22:40,350 --> 00:22:41,270
Alright.

333
00:22:42,350 --> 00:22:43,440
I know

334
00:22:44,110 --> 00:22:45,250
you men

335
00:22:45,280 --> 00:22:47,880
have no patience
for all these formalities.

336
00:22:48,350 --> 00:22:49,790
Go on and leave

337
00:22:50,680 --> 00:22:52,650
so we ladies can have a good talk.

338
00:22:53,640 --> 00:22:54,290
Yes, Mother.

339
00:22:54,290 --> 00:22:55,160
Yes, Mother.

340
00:22:55,640 --> 00:22:56,480
Mother,

341
00:22:56,750 --> 00:22:58,750
I hardly think you actually want to chat.

342
00:22:58,750 --> 00:23:01,750
You're just eager to
set up the card table, aren't you?

343
00:23:01,830 --> 00:23:03,780
You needn't rush.

344
00:23:03,960 --> 00:23:04,720
This time,

345
00:23:04,750 --> 00:23:06,680
I've brought a whole box of silver.

346
00:23:06,680 --> 00:23:08,920
You may win to your heart's content.

347
00:23:09,030 --> 00:23:10,090
And if all my money

348
00:23:10,120 --> 00:23:11,320
ends up in your hands,

349
00:23:11,440 --> 00:23:13,500
there's still Third Sister-in-law.

350
00:23:13,920 --> 00:23:15,980
She's the real one with deep pockets.

351
00:23:16,070 --> 00:23:17,440
You cheeky little thing.

352
00:23:17,440 --> 00:23:19,170
I ought to pinch your lips shut!

353
00:23:21,590 --> 00:23:22,200
Mother.

354
00:23:24,110 --> 00:23:25,640
After you, Second Brother.

355
00:23:38,110 --> 00:23:39,510
Second Brother, please.

356
00:23:39,590 --> 00:23:40,070
Okay.

357
00:23:40,680 --> 00:23:41,740
Thank you, Yanyun.

358
00:23:43,920 --> 00:23:45,250
Thank you, Third Uncle.

359
00:23:45,920 --> 00:23:46,750
Back then,

360
00:23:47,070 --> 00:23:48,270
when Lady Jiang died,

361
00:23:48,960 --> 00:23:49,880
you told Mother

362
00:23:50,000 --> 00:23:51,790
you wished to observe mourning rites

363
00:23:51,790 --> 00:23:53,120
and refused to remarry.

364
00:23:53,880 --> 00:23:55,030
And you kept that observance

365
00:23:55,030 --> 00:23:56,200
all these years.

366
00:23:57,640 --> 00:23:58,650
I'd thought

367
00:23:58,720 --> 00:24:00,320
you would never marry again.

368
00:24:00,920 --> 00:24:01,980
Yes, Yanzhang.

369
00:24:02,110 --> 00:24:03,000
Even I myself

370
00:24:03,310 --> 00:24:04,710
didn't expect it either.

371
00:24:05,160 --> 00:24:06,150
Yes, Yanyun.

372
00:24:06,270 --> 00:24:06,960
How exactly

373
00:24:07,000 --> 00:24:08,280
did you and Lady Gu

374
00:24:08,310 --> 00:24:09,110
get together?

375
00:24:10,510 --> 00:24:11,440
Surely it wasn't the Ji family

376
00:24:11,440 --> 00:24:12,880
deliberately presenting her to you

377
00:24:12,880 --> 00:24:14,440
to ensnare you?

378
00:24:16,550 --> 00:24:18,550
What nonsense are you talking about?

379
00:24:18,550 --> 00:24:19,480
Since your third brother has

380
00:24:19,480 --> 00:24:20,410
married Lady Gu,

381
00:24:20,830 --> 00:24:22,490
he naturally has his reasons.

382
00:24:22,680 --> 00:24:24,080
Don't speak carelessly.

383
00:24:24,440 --> 00:24:25,270
Where

384
00:24:26,350 --> 00:24:27,750
did you hear such things?

385
00:24:28,920 --> 00:24:29,720
I...

386
00:24:32,270 --> 00:24:33,590
I heard it from people outside.

387
00:24:33,590 --> 00:24:34,850
Which people outside?

388
00:24:40,350 --> 00:24:41,410
I don't want to hear

389
00:24:42,700 --> 00:24:44,700
this kind of talk a second time.

390
00:24:46,720 --> 00:24:47,720
I know I was wrong.

391
00:24:52,030 --> 00:24:53,400
As for Lady Gu and me...

392
00:24:55,070 --> 00:24:56,130
how should I put it?

393
00:24:57,240 --> 00:24:58,270
It should be—

394
00:24:58,830 --> 00:25:00,720
our hearts entwined the moment we met,

395
00:25:00,720 --> 00:25:02,850
but fate brought us together too late.

396
00:25:05,270 --> 00:25:07,030
This is the first time I've ever seen you

397
00:25:07,030 --> 00:25:08,480
so deeply devoted.

398
00:25:09,240 --> 00:25:10,680
It seems that my third sister-in-law

399
00:25:10,680 --> 00:25:11,880
is no ordinary woman.

400
00:25:13,750 --> 00:25:14,440
But

401
00:25:14,720 --> 00:25:15,520
rest assured.

402
00:25:16,350 --> 00:25:18,810
Since she's the woman
you cherish so dearly,

403
00:25:18,960 --> 00:25:20,690
no one in this entire household

404
00:25:21,030 --> 00:25:21,750
will dare let her

405
00:25:21,750 --> 00:25:23,830
suffer even the slightest grievance.

406
00:25:23,830 --> 00:25:25,110
Since I've married her,

407
00:25:25,110 --> 00:25:25,830
naturally,

408
00:25:26,110 --> 00:25:27,640
I won't let her suffer any grievances.

409
00:25:27,640 --> 00:25:28,550
Of course.

410
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:31,260
When I saw the grandeur

411
00:25:31,350 --> 00:25:33,030
of your wedding procession yesterday,

412
00:25:33,030 --> 00:25:34,000
oh my,

413
00:25:34,790 --> 00:25:36,440
it would've been grand enough to welcome

414
00:25:36,440 --> 00:25:37,970
a princess into the family.

415
00:25:39,510 --> 00:25:40,570
By the way, Yanyun,

416
00:25:41,510 --> 00:25:42,570
there is something

417
00:25:42,960 --> 00:25:44,020
I wanted to ask you.

418
00:25:44,110 --> 00:25:45,640
Please go ahead, Yanzhang.

419
00:25:53,790 --> 00:25:54,680
I just remembered

420
00:25:54,680 --> 00:25:56,110
the shop manager came earlier.

421
00:25:56,110 --> 00:25:57,750
Maybe there's something wrong at the shop.

422
00:25:57,750 --> 00:25:59,200
Yanzhang, Yanyun,

423
00:25:59,440 --> 00:26:00,240
you guys talk first.

424
00:26:00,240 --> 00:26:01,300
I'll go take a look.

425
00:26:01,750 --> 00:26:02,310
Go ahead.

426
00:26:03,310 --> 00:26:04,000
Then I will

427
00:26:04,310 --> 00:26:05,240
head back first.

428
00:26:26,200 --> 00:26:27,130
Are you alright?

429
00:26:29,110 --> 00:26:29,640
What?

430
00:26:30,960 --> 00:26:32,640
You don't look so well.

431
00:26:35,070 --> 00:26:35,670
Is that so?

432
00:26:36,440 --> 00:26:38,790
Perhaps I didn't rest well last night.

433
00:26:42,240 --> 00:26:43,650
How could you rest well?

434
00:26:43,880 --> 00:26:45,550
There they are discussing court affairs,

435
00:26:45,550 --> 00:26:46,960
and it's understandable to
shut out someone like me

436
00:26:46,960 --> 00:26:48,160
who only handles family business.

437
00:26:48,160 --> 00:26:49,970
But you are a dignified Tanhua,

438
00:26:50,160 --> 00:26:51,270
a future Grand Secretary.

439
00:26:51,270 --> 00:26:52,870
And yet they shut you out too.

440
00:26:54,590 --> 00:26:56,390
I really feel it's unfair to you.

441
00:26:57,440 --> 00:26:58,770
You jest, Fourth Uncle.

442
00:26:59,270 --> 00:27:00,240
I'm a junior.

443
00:27:00,590 --> 00:27:01,960
When elders are discussing matters,

444
00:27:01,960 --> 00:27:03,920
I naturally shouldn't get involved.

445
00:27:03,920 --> 00:27:05,920
How could I possibly feel slighted?

446
00:27:07,790 --> 00:27:08,990
Oh, right, Xuanqing.

447
00:27:09,270 --> 00:27:10,400
You also attended Lady Gu's

448
00:27:10,400 --> 00:27:11,860
coming-of-age ceremony.

449
00:27:12,310 --> 00:27:15,570
So was it really the Ji family
offering her to Yanyun or not?

450
00:27:15,640 --> 00:27:16,440
Of course not.

451
00:27:17,200 --> 00:27:17,880
Really?

452
00:27:18,240 --> 00:27:18,720
Really.

453
00:27:23,030 --> 00:27:24,350
Now that's strange.

454
00:27:24,720 --> 00:27:26,070
If it weren't for her,

455
00:27:27,440 --> 00:27:28,900
how could your Third Uncle

456
00:27:28,960 --> 00:27:29,640
have cared

457
00:27:29,640 --> 00:27:31,160
so much for the Ji family?

458
00:27:32,270 --> 00:27:34,030
Just the land reform case alone—

459
00:27:34,030 --> 00:27:34,680
there was no way the Ji family

460
00:27:34,680 --> 00:27:36,750
could've come out unscathed.

461
00:27:39,240 --> 00:27:41,030
I don't know why Third Uncle

462
00:27:41,510 --> 00:27:43,170
showed favor to the Ji family.

463
00:27:43,500 --> 00:27:45,590
But during the days
of Lady Gu's coming-of-age ceremony,

464
00:27:45,590 --> 00:27:46,270
Third Uncle was with me

465
00:27:46,270 --> 00:27:47,200
the whole time.

466
00:27:47,480 --> 00:27:48,240
He never once

467
00:27:48,240 --> 00:27:49,310
met her alone,

468
00:27:49,780 --> 00:27:52,780
much less anything like
the Ji family offering her up.

469
00:27:55,310 --> 00:27:56,000
You truly are someone

470
00:27:56,000 --> 00:27:58,200
your Third Uncle brought home himself.

471
00:27:59,250 --> 00:28:00,050
Alright then.

472
00:28:00,270 --> 00:28:01,870
If it wasn't, then it wasn't.

473
00:28:02,030 --> 00:28:03,680
He's a Grand Secretary, after all.

474
00:28:03,680 --> 00:28:04,940
Whatever he says goes.

475
00:28:05,960 --> 00:28:06,440
I'm off.

476
00:28:14,070 --> 00:28:14,670
Yunting.

477
00:28:15,400 --> 00:28:16,200
Young Master.

478
00:28:17,440 --> 00:28:18,200
I keep feeling

479
00:28:18,200 --> 00:28:19,630
that something is off with Fourth Uncle.

480
00:28:19,630 --> 00:28:20,640
Think of a way

481
00:28:21,000 --> 00:28:22,660
to keep an eye on him secretly.

482
00:28:22,960 --> 00:28:23,440
Okay.

483
00:28:27,750 --> 00:28:29,390
Yanyun is something else.

484
00:28:29,550 --> 00:28:31,950
It's only the second day
after his wedding,

485
00:28:32,240 --> 00:28:34,840
and he's rushed out
first thing in the morning.

486
00:28:36,240 --> 00:28:37,200
Mother,

487
00:28:37,480 --> 00:28:39,080
Yanyun had official duties.

488
00:28:39,200 --> 00:28:40,920
Someone from the palace
came early in the morning.

489
00:28:40,920 --> 00:28:42,520
If it was official business,

490
00:28:43,480 --> 00:28:45,400
why did he take Zhao along?

491
00:28:46,070 --> 00:28:47,670
Listen to yourself, Mother.

492
00:28:47,680 --> 00:28:49,110
Yanyun dotes on his wife.

493
00:28:49,480 --> 00:28:50,680
That's a good thing.

494
00:28:50,680 --> 00:28:51,350
Doting on his wife

495
00:28:51,350 --> 00:28:52,760
is all well and good,
but not to this extent!

496
00:28:52,760 --> 00:28:55,220
Especially with all those rumors around...

497
00:29:05,400 --> 00:29:06,440
I mean...

498
00:29:07,590 --> 00:29:09,440
Yanyun is willful.

499
00:29:09,920 --> 00:29:11,850
You should've talked him out of it.

500
00:29:12,880 --> 00:29:14,810
Why did you go along?

501
00:29:16,310 --> 00:29:17,160
Because...

502
00:29:17,830 --> 00:29:19,630
I wanted to go in the first place.

503
00:29:24,920 --> 00:29:26,440
Mother, you might not know this.

504
00:29:26,440 --> 00:29:27,970
When I came here yesterday,

505
00:29:28,110 --> 00:29:29,310
I happened to encounter

506
00:29:29,310 --> 00:29:30,750
the Marquis Changxing's household

507
00:29:30,750 --> 00:29:32,150
transporting the coffin

508
00:29:32,200 --> 00:29:34,070
to Xuanmiao Temple on South Gate Street.

509
00:29:34,070 --> 00:29:36,590
By all rights, the deceased
take precedence,

510
00:29:36,590 --> 00:29:38,720
and we should have made way—

511
00:29:39,160 --> 00:29:42,070
especially given that
it was the Marquis's household.

512
00:29:42,070 --> 00:29:43,110
But unexpectedly,

513
00:29:43,110 --> 00:29:43,920
they

514
00:29:44,110 --> 00:29:45,440
made way for us first.

515
00:29:45,920 --> 00:29:47,070
So I've felt

516
00:29:47,240 --> 00:29:49,170
deeply uneasy about it ever since.

517
00:29:49,310 --> 00:29:50,370
And as it happened,

518
00:29:50,480 --> 00:29:51,610
early this morning,

519
00:29:51,790 --> 00:29:53,510
His Majesty ordered Yanyun

520
00:29:53,510 --> 00:29:55,200
to offer incense to the Marquis.

521
00:29:55,200 --> 00:29:56,160
So I thought

522
00:29:56,240 --> 00:29:57,730
I should go along

523
00:29:58,030 --> 00:29:59,030
and offer incense

524
00:29:59,400 --> 00:30:00,880
for the Marquis myself as well.

525
00:30:00,880 --> 00:30:01,830
You are just

526
00:30:01,960 --> 00:30:04,160
too sincere-hearted for your own good.

527
00:30:08,440 --> 00:30:10,240
Mother, Second Sister-in-law.

528
00:30:13,680 --> 00:30:15,440
It was clearly His Majesty's decree.

529
00:30:15,440 --> 00:30:17,500
Why did you take it all upon yourself?

530
00:30:17,590 --> 00:30:18,980
It was His Majesty

531
00:30:19,160 --> 00:30:21,090
who ordered Zhao to accompany you?

532
00:30:22,310 --> 00:30:22,890
Well...

533
00:30:23,350 --> 00:30:25,160
How could that be possible?

534
00:30:25,440 --> 00:30:26,030
Mother,

535
00:30:26,240 --> 00:30:27,750
that was an imperial decree.

536
00:30:27,750 --> 00:30:29,750
It's not something we should question.

537
00:30:29,750 --> 00:30:30,810
Alright, alright.

538
00:30:30,830 --> 00:30:32,240
I won't ask anymore.

539
00:30:34,310 --> 00:30:36,340
There's news from Shanxi.

540
00:30:36,640 --> 00:30:37,370
How about...

541
00:30:38,590 --> 00:30:40,250
you go and help me look into it?

542
00:30:40,640 --> 00:30:42,290
There's news from Shanxi?

543
00:30:42,510 --> 00:30:43,770
Then let's go quickly.

544
00:30:45,240 --> 00:30:45,810
Mother.

545
00:30:46,070 --> 00:30:46,590
Mother.

546
00:30:54,070 --> 00:30:55,830
Why does he also need

547
00:30:56,510 --> 00:30:58,710
Zhao to help with the affairs in Shanxi?

548
00:31:00,830 --> 00:31:01,860
I heard

549
00:31:01,920 --> 00:31:04,080
Jinzhao has business there.

550
00:31:04,550 --> 00:31:06,370
She even donated grain and money

551
00:31:06,440 --> 00:31:08,440
when Pingyang was struck
by a severe drought.

552
00:31:08,440 --> 00:31:09,970
Yes, I heard that too.

553
00:31:10,070 --> 00:31:10,750
Didn't

554
00:31:10,750 --> 00:31:13,080
His Majesty commend her
for it at the time?

555
00:31:13,670 --> 00:31:15,070
With so many businesses,

556
00:31:15,110 --> 00:31:16,880
a young, newlywed wife like her

557
00:31:17,790 --> 00:31:19,920
is even busier than a grand secretary.

558
00:31:24,640 --> 00:31:26,270
You're really good at making things up.

559
00:31:26,270 --> 00:31:27,310
What did I make up?

560
00:31:28,270 --> 00:31:29,030
You actually claimed

561
00:31:29,030 --> 00:31:30,760
that was His Majesty's decree.

562
00:31:30,790 --> 00:31:33,850
Does that count as
falsely invoking an imperial order?

563
00:31:36,000 --> 00:31:37,800
You'll say anything, won't you?

564
00:31:41,490 --> 00:31:43,890
Well, you said
it was His Majesty's decree.

565
00:31:44,750 --> 00:31:45,640
Tell me,

566
00:31:46,460 --> 00:31:48,000
did His Majesty order me

567
00:31:48,000 --> 00:31:50,800
to offer incense
at Marquis Changxing's Mansion?

568
00:31:51,510 --> 00:31:52,460
His Majesty's decree

569
00:31:52,460 --> 00:31:53,370
indeed said so.

570
00:31:53,880 --> 00:31:54,880
And all I said was,

571
00:31:54,960 --> 00:31:56,960
"It was clearly His Majesty's order."

572
00:31:56,960 --> 00:31:58,270
What was wrong with that?

573
00:31:58,270 --> 00:31:59,160
How are you

574
00:31:59,400 --> 00:32:00,830
so full of tricks?

575
00:32:03,590 --> 00:32:05,120
You're no less so yourself.

576
00:32:06,960 --> 00:32:08,030
I only said

577
00:32:08,030 --> 00:32:09,310
that news had come from Shanxi,

578
00:32:09,310 --> 00:32:10,840
yet you played right along.

579
00:32:10,880 --> 00:32:12,480
Well, you'd already come to pick me up.

580
00:32:12,480 --> 00:32:13,720
If I hadn't left with you,

581
00:32:13,720 --> 00:32:14,640
I'd be stupid.

582
00:32:15,230 --> 00:32:17,490
You walked away rather quickly just now.

583
00:32:20,310 --> 00:32:22,680
You've suffered grievances because of me.

584
00:32:22,680 --> 00:32:23,970
Those things

585
00:32:24,070 --> 00:32:25,070
are nothing to me.

586
00:32:26,200 --> 00:32:27,070
Mother

587
00:32:27,550 --> 00:32:28,830
is not a bad person at heart.

588
00:32:28,830 --> 00:32:29,830
It's just that our marriage

589
00:32:29,830 --> 00:32:31,160
wasn't arranged by her,

590
00:32:31,240 --> 00:32:33,160
so she's just displeased.

591
00:32:34,020 --> 00:32:35,330
Most of it falls on me.

592
00:32:35,510 --> 00:32:38,240
I'm sorry that you've been
caught up in it as well.

593
00:32:38,480 --> 00:32:39,480
But fortunately,

594
00:32:40,680 --> 00:32:41,750
Mother is

595
00:32:41,920 --> 00:32:43,720
a bit of a snob.

596
00:32:44,350 --> 00:32:45,550
Seeing that I've

597
00:32:45,920 --> 00:32:47,850
brought honor to the whole family,

598
00:32:47,920 --> 00:32:49,310
she won't do anything unreasonable.

599
00:32:49,310 --> 00:32:50,440
Oh my,

600
00:32:50,750 --> 00:32:51,880
you're actually calling Mother

601
00:32:51,880 --> 00:32:53,340
snobbish behind her back?

602
00:32:53,790 --> 00:32:54,750
Later,

603
00:32:55,000 --> 00:32:56,720
I'll secretly tell her.

604
00:32:57,880 --> 00:32:58,640
Really?

605
00:33:02,080 --> 00:33:03,160
You're asking for trouble.

606
00:33:03,160 --> 00:33:04,310
Put me down.

607
00:33:20,070 --> 00:33:22,130
I'll talk. I'll tell you everything!

608
00:33:43,000 --> 00:33:44,240
Ye Xian! Ye Xian!

609
00:33:45,110 --> 00:33:46,910
I'll tell you everything I know!

610
00:33:46,990 --> 00:33:47,840
Everything.

611
00:33:48,160 --> 00:33:48,960
Just let me go.

612
00:33:51,160 --> 00:33:51,690
Alright.

613
00:33:53,000 --> 00:33:53,800
Wang Xuanfan!

614
00:33:54,240 --> 00:33:55,240
Wang Xuanfan has ties...

615
00:33:55,240 --> 00:33:57,370
has ties with the bandits in Shandong!

616
00:34:00,440 --> 00:34:00,840
And...

617
00:34:02,120 --> 00:34:04,050
In the disaster relief grain case,

618
00:34:04,270 --> 00:34:05,870
that Secretary surnamed Sun

619
00:34:06,880 --> 00:34:08,480
was killed by the men he sent.

620
00:34:12,800 --> 00:34:13,320
Also,

621
00:34:14,440 --> 00:34:15,699
in Daming Prefecture,

622
00:34:16,070 --> 00:34:18,060
he's concealed over 1,000 men

623
00:34:18,150 --> 00:34:19,840
and tens of thousands of acres
of fertile land.

624
00:34:19,840 --> 00:34:20,699
Anything else?

625
00:34:21,590 --> 00:34:22,110
Also...

626
00:34:24,790 --> 00:34:26,790
The wealthy merchants in Shanxi...

627
00:34:27,670 --> 00:34:28,620
On the surface,

628
00:34:28,639 --> 00:34:30,320
he accepts their bribes.

629
00:34:31,230 --> 00:34:32,360
But in secret,

630
00:34:32,840 --> 00:34:33,920
he's been colluding and trading

631
00:34:33,920 --> 00:34:34,989
with the northern tribes

632
00:34:34,989 --> 00:34:36,030
through them!

633
00:34:42,670 --> 00:34:43,409
What else?

634
00:34:43,710 --> 00:34:45,310
That's it. That's all I know.

635
00:34:59,440 --> 00:35:00,670
Ye Xian!

636
00:35:01,280 --> 00:35:02,920
I'll kill you!

637
00:35:06,110 --> 00:35:06,890
Let go of me!

638
00:35:07,150 --> 00:35:08,150
Ye Xian!

639
00:35:14,710 --> 00:35:17,190
Zhang Ling, the former Commander
of the Penal Court,

640
00:35:17,190 --> 00:35:19,030
has admitted that his crimes were grave.

641
00:35:19,030 --> 00:35:20,160
By His Majesty's secret decree,

642
00:35:20,160 --> 00:35:22,000
he is hereby sentenced to execution.

643
00:35:22,000 --> 00:35:23,840
Throw his body into the mass grave

644
00:35:23,840 --> 00:35:24,500
and bury it.

645
00:35:25,480 --> 00:35:26,110
Yes, sir!

646
00:35:38,920 --> 00:35:40,230
Zhang Ling is dead?

647
00:35:40,590 --> 00:35:41,030
Yes.

648
00:35:41,360 --> 00:35:43,760
They say
he committed suicide out of guilt.

649
00:35:45,880 --> 00:35:46,710
Impossible.

650
00:35:47,960 --> 00:35:49,690
He valued his life too much to die.

651
00:35:49,690 --> 00:35:50,340
Then...

652
00:35:50,630 --> 00:35:51,840
could it be because the Ye family

653
00:35:51,840 --> 00:35:53,370
was stripped of their title

654
00:35:53,710 --> 00:35:55,310
that Ye Xian, in a fit of rage,

655
00:35:55,550 --> 00:35:56,670
took his anger out on Zhang Ling?

656
00:35:56,670 --> 00:35:57,800
Did you see the body?

657
00:35:59,590 --> 00:36:00,230
Well...

658
00:36:01,000 --> 00:36:02,030
The Xuanfeng Guards

659
00:36:02,030 --> 00:36:03,840
are all personally selected
by His Majesty.

660
00:36:03,840 --> 00:36:04,590
Our people

661
00:36:04,590 --> 00:36:07,000
haven't had the chance
to be planted inside yet.

662
00:36:07,000 --> 00:36:07,460
Master,

663
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:08,990
are you suspecting

664
00:36:09,070 --> 00:36:09,510
that it was him...

665
00:36:09,510 --> 00:36:10,150
Master!

666
00:36:12,280 --> 00:36:13,150
The Wang family had someone

667
00:36:13,150 --> 00:36:14,230
deliver the guest list for next month's

668
00:36:14,230 --> 00:36:15,090
tea gathering.

669
00:36:15,110 --> 00:36:17,440
As expected, there was
no sign of Gu Jin...

670
00:36:17,550 --> 00:36:18,480
Jinzhao's name.

671
00:36:35,320 --> 00:36:36,670
I've loaded Master's luggage
onto the cart.

672
00:36:36,670 --> 00:36:38,870
Take good care of Master on the journey.

673
00:36:38,920 --> 00:36:40,380
Rest assured, Changshun.

674
00:36:46,110 --> 00:36:47,710
You needn't wait any longer.

675
00:36:48,320 --> 00:36:49,880
Today is the Eldest Miss's
first return home after her wedding.

676
00:36:49,880 --> 00:36:51,710
No one from the family
will come to see you off.

677
00:36:51,710 --> 00:36:52,960
It's just me.

678
00:36:53,320 --> 00:36:55,650
But they shouldn't just
send no one at all.

679
00:36:58,550 --> 00:36:59,320
Master,

680
00:36:59,800 --> 00:37:00,510
go.

681
00:37:01,190 --> 00:37:02,850
The road to Pingyang is rough.

682
00:37:03,110 --> 00:37:05,170
We mustn't be late for taking office.

683
00:37:22,150 --> 00:37:24,150
"Had you known it would end this way,

684
00:37:24,480 --> 00:37:26,680
would you still have done what you did?"

685
00:37:27,800 --> 00:37:29,700
It's too late

686
00:37:29,730 --> 00:37:31,700
to regret it now.

687
00:37:37,070 --> 00:37:37,670
Go.

688
00:37:38,190 --> 00:37:39,510
Take good care of Master on the road.

689
00:37:39,510 --> 00:37:40,070
Will do!

690
00:37:40,510 --> 00:37:40,960
Hyah!

691
00:37:45,920 --> 00:37:49,580
[Gu]

692
00:37:46,590 --> 00:37:48,110
What time is it already?

693
00:37:48,230 --> 00:37:49,890
Why haven't they arrived yet?

694
00:37:50,000 --> 00:37:51,840
Quick, send someone to check

695
00:37:51,840 --> 00:37:52,790
where they are!

696
00:37:52,920 --> 00:37:54,760
I've already sent someone.

697
00:37:55,440 --> 00:37:57,590
Now that Zhao's become
a Grand Secretary's wife,

698
00:37:57,590 --> 00:37:59,440
she's certainly putting on airs—

699
00:37:59,440 --> 00:38:00,510
making the whole family

700
00:38:00,510 --> 00:38:01,770
wait for her like this.

701
00:38:02,000 --> 00:38:04,530
Isn't she afraid of
using up her good fortune?

702
00:38:05,800 --> 00:38:07,070
Old Madam, Old Madam!

703
00:38:09,550 --> 00:38:10,110
Well?

704
00:38:10,480 --> 00:38:11,340
Where are they?

705
00:38:11,360 --> 00:38:12,920
They're...

706
00:38:13,110 --> 00:38:13,800
Spit it out!

707
00:38:13,800 --> 00:38:14,320
Well...

708
00:38:14,920 --> 00:38:16,070
O-Old Madam, Master,

709
00:38:16,070 --> 00:38:16,630
Madam,

710
00:38:17,630 --> 00:38:19,160
Eldest Miss and her husband

711
00:38:19,440 --> 00:38:20,570
aren't coming here.

712
00:38:21,630 --> 00:38:22,890
Then where did they go?

713
00:38:23,840 --> 00:38:24,710
They said

714
00:38:25,030 --> 00:38:26,490
they've gone to Tongzhou.

715
00:38:27,090 --> 00:38:28,070
Tongzhou?

716
00:38:28,800 --> 00:38:29,280
Well...

717
00:38:30,030 --> 00:38:30,960
What about Rong?

718
00:38:30,960 --> 00:38:33,220
Is he still at the Qifang Hutong Academy?

719
00:38:33,280 --> 00:38:34,130
I asked.

720
00:38:34,230 --> 00:38:35,230
Young Master Rong

721
00:38:35,230 --> 00:38:36,510
left the academy yesterday

722
00:38:36,510 --> 00:38:38,040
and went to Tongzhou first.

723
00:38:39,680 --> 00:38:44,500
[Gu]

724
00:38:40,550 --> 00:38:41,150
You...

725
00:38:46,190 --> 00:38:47,190
Let's go back too.

726
00:38:47,400 --> 00:38:48,730
-Yes, My Lady.
-Mother.

727
00:38:49,230 --> 00:38:49,760
Gu Lan!

728
00:38:53,830 --> 00:38:55,540
Did you know all along

729
00:38:55,700 --> 00:38:56,690
that Gu Jinzhao

730
00:38:56,880 --> 00:38:58,340
wasn't coming back today?

731
00:38:58,400 --> 00:38:59,600
How would I know that?

732
00:39:00,920 --> 00:39:02,620
Stop pretending.

733
00:39:03,510 --> 00:39:04,590
Do you think

734
00:39:04,620 --> 00:39:06,150
that with Gu Jinzhao marrying Chen Yanyun,

735
00:39:06,150 --> 00:39:08,510
you'll get to rise in status
along with her?

736
00:39:08,510 --> 00:39:09,410
Lian.

737
00:39:09,550 --> 00:39:10,480
Stop dreaming.

738
00:39:10,740 --> 00:39:12,510
She doesn't care about you at all.

739
00:39:12,510 --> 00:39:13,510
She's long taken Rong

740
00:39:13,510 --> 00:39:14,110
back to Tongzhou,

741
00:39:14,110 --> 00:39:15,440
leaving you here alone.

742
00:39:17,440 --> 00:39:19,220
Tongzhou is Zhao's maternal family.

743
00:39:19,220 --> 00:39:20,800
It's only natural
that she wouldn't take me along.

744
00:39:20,800 --> 00:39:21,940
So what if I'm alone?

745
00:39:22,080 --> 00:39:23,650
Can't I live my life alone?

746
00:39:23,920 --> 00:39:24,880
I have my own ways

747
00:39:24,880 --> 00:39:25,710
of getting by.

748
00:39:34,590 --> 00:39:35,670
-Go.
-Go.

749
00:39:36,510 --> 00:39:38,480
The nerve of you!

750
00:39:48,110 --> 00:39:48,920
Oh, you.

751
00:39:49,230 --> 00:39:51,430
If you don't want to go back, just don't.

752
00:39:51,560 --> 00:39:53,510
Why did you intentionally not tell them?

753
00:39:53,510 --> 00:39:55,480
If I had told Grandmother in advance,

754
00:39:55,480 --> 00:39:56,740
with her temperament,

755
00:39:56,920 --> 00:39:58,760
she would certainly have
invoked family ethics and filial duty

756
00:39:58,760 --> 00:39:59,620
to pressure me.

757
00:40:00,590 --> 00:40:01,440
And then,

758
00:40:01,670 --> 00:40:03,150
for the sake of your reputation,

759
00:40:03,150 --> 00:40:04,950
I'd have no choice but to give in.

760
00:40:05,280 --> 00:40:07,190
So it was better not to tell her at all—

761
00:40:07,190 --> 00:40:08,790
act first, inform her after,

762
00:40:08,800 --> 00:40:10,460
and leave her no time to react.

763
00:40:10,670 --> 00:40:11,590
So in the end,

764
00:40:12,030 --> 00:40:13,230
it's my fault.

765
00:40:13,760 --> 00:40:14,590
Yes.

766
00:40:16,440 --> 00:40:18,630
Just because you're
a dignified Grand Secretary,

767
00:40:18,630 --> 00:40:19,800
in everything you do,

768
00:40:19,800 --> 00:40:21,550
you have to be a model for others.

769
00:40:21,550 --> 00:40:22,360
Therefore, there are so many things

770
00:40:22,360 --> 00:40:23,440
I can no longer do.

771
00:40:26,070 --> 00:40:26,670
Oh?

772
00:40:28,880 --> 00:40:30,410
And what is it you wish to do?

773
00:40:34,600 --> 00:40:36,760
♪ Ask the passing time
whether it has forgotten ♪

774
00:40:37,500 --> 00:40:39,090
♪ The moonlight of our first encounter ♪

775
00:40:40,270 --> 00:40:43,690
♪ Year after year,
it etches your likeness ♪

776
00:40:44,600 --> 00:40:46,980
♪ Count the faint shimmer
of the starry river ♪

777
00:40:48,170 --> 00:40:51,760
♪ Yet none compares
to the gentle light in your eyes ♪

778
00:40:52,880 --> 00:40:54,730
♪ At last, I see the galaxy
shimmering and swaying ♪

779
00:40:55,600 --> 00:40:57,200
♪ Reflected in our eyes ♪

780
00:40:58,290 --> 00:41:02,910
♪ I'll be with you forever ♪

781
00:41:04,070 --> 00:41:07,690
♪ And enjoy
the beautiful scenery with you ♪

782
00:41:09,790 --> 00:41:13,300
♪ For all the days of our lives,
our love will endure ♪

783
00:41:11,590 --> 00:41:12,190
Oh, right.

784
00:41:12,760 --> 00:41:14,360
At the banquet the other day,

785
00:41:14,630 --> 00:41:16,120
Mu mentioned

786
00:41:16,230 --> 00:41:17,290
that his eldest son

787
00:41:17,360 --> 00:41:18,960
wishes to seek your third sister's hand
in marriage.

788
00:41:18,960 --> 00:41:20,090
What a mood-killer.

789
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:26,550
The eldest son of the Mu family,

790
00:41:26,550 --> 00:41:27,510
Mu Zhidi?

791
00:41:30,230 --> 00:41:31,480
Before my mother passed away,

792
00:41:31,480 --> 00:41:33,230
he'd already brought it up once.

793
00:41:33,230 --> 00:41:33,960
But

794
00:41:33,960 --> 00:41:35,400
that was three years ago.

795
00:41:36,920 --> 00:41:37,960
I thought Young Master Mu

796
00:41:37,960 --> 00:41:39,560
had already been betrothed.

797
00:41:40,550 --> 00:41:41,480
I'm afraid

798
00:41:41,710 --> 00:41:43,170
this match won't work out.

799
00:41:45,110 --> 00:41:45,880
At that time,

800
00:41:46,000 --> 00:41:47,600
Lan had already refused him.

801
00:41:47,840 --> 00:41:48,700
Besides,

802
00:41:49,000 --> 00:41:51,930
she found Young Master Mu
looked too simple-minded.

803
00:41:52,360 --> 00:41:53,590
Corrupt official, get out!

804
00:41:53,590 --> 00:41:55,210
Give us an explanation!

805
00:41:55,360 --> 00:41:56,710
-Get out!
-Give us an explanation!

806
00:41:56,710 --> 00:41:57,670
Corrupt official!

807
00:41:57,670 --> 00:41:59,000
Explain yourself to us!

808
00:41:59,000 --> 00:42:00,190
Corrupt official, get out

809
00:42:00,190 --> 00:42:01,430
and explain!

810
00:42:01,630 --> 00:42:02,430
Third Master,

811
00:42:02,590 --> 00:42:04,230
there are seven or eight
young scholars ahead

812
00:42:04,230 --> 00:42:05,360
blocking the road with banners.

813
00:42:05,360 --> 00:42:06,190
They read:

814
00:42:07,000 --> 00:42:09,440
"Unjust land reform—
all under heaven cries out."

815
00:42:09,440 --> 00:42:10,630
They also mention imperial lands

816
00:42:10,630 --> 00:42:11,690
and noble estates.

817
00:42:12,230 --> 00:42:13,920
Get out now, corrupt official!

818
00:42:13,920 --> 00:42:15,510
This feels rather suspicious.

819
00:42:15,510 --> 00:42:17,190
I'll go take a look. Wait here.

820
00:42:17,510 --> 00:42:18,190
Okay.

821
00:42:18,440 --> 00:42:19,670
Be careful then.

822
00:42:22,670 --> 00:42:23,920
Give us an explanation!

823
00:42:23,920 --> 00:42:25,110
We deserve an explanation!

824
00:42:25,110 --> 00:42:26,170
Corrupt official,

825
00:42:26,440 --> 00:42:27,190
give us an explanation!

826
00:42:27,190 --> 00:42:28,070
Seize them all

827
00:42:28,230 --> 00:42:29,550
and question them one by one.

828
00:42:29,550 --> 00:42:30,210
Squat down!

829
00:42:31,230 --> 00:42:32,560
Take them further away.

830
00:42:33,030 --> 00:42:34,550
-Don't startle the Madam.
-Get down! Down!

831
00:42:34,550 --> 00:42:35,070
Yes.

832
00:42:35,590 --> 00:42:36,190
My Lady.

833
00:42:36,710 --> 00:42:37,840
These scholars

834
00:42:38,150 --> 00:42:38,710
actually knew

835
00:42:38,710 --> 00:42:39,920
we would pass by here.

836
00:42:40,510 --> 00:42:42,550
Someone must have instructed them.

837
00:42:44,840 --> 00:42:47,000
There is no shortage of people
who resent Yanyun.

838
00:42:47,000 --> 00:42:47,360
But

839
00:42:47,360 --> 00:42:49,110
those capable of stirring up scholars
to cause

840
00:42:49,110 --> 00:42:50,710
this kind of trouble are few.

841
00:43:01,070 --> 00:43:01,870
Third Master,

842
00:43:01,880 --> 00:43:03,000
that fellow confessed.

843
00:43:03,000 --> 00:43:04,670
It was a servant
from Wang Xuanfan's household

844
00:43:04,670 --> 00:43:06,360
who instructed them
to remonstrate with you

845
00:43:06,360 --> 00:43:07,150
and revealed our whereabouts

846
00:43:07,150 --> 00:43:07,880
to them.

847
00:43:10,510 --> 00:43:11,530
Wang Xuanfan...

848
00:43:11,800 --> 00:43:13,760
I made him pay
tens of thousands more taels in taxes,

849
00:43:13,760 --> 00:43:15,890
and it seems he's come to truly hate me.

850
00:43:16,070 --> 00:43:16,670
Well then,

851
00:43:17,510 --> 00:43:18,710
assign two men

852
00:43:19,150 --> 00:43:21,550
to escort them back to the capital
and have them detained.

853
00:43:21,550 --> 00:43:22,750
Treat them properly.

854
00:43:23,150 --> 00:43:24,480
As for everything else,

855
